[b]Moyers &amp; Company, February 3 2012: How Do Conservatives and Liberals See the World[/b]

1) [u]How Do Conservatives and Liberals See the World?[/u]

Bill talks with social psychologist Jonathan Haidt about the moral underpinnings of our contentious culture.

2) [u]Bill Moyers Essay: Newt Gingrich and the Real Saul Alinsky[/u]

Bill Moyers explains what we need to know about the community activist, and why New Gingrich might be so afraid of him.


